| ---- | --------------------- |
| 200  | Success               |
| 201  | Resource Created      |
| 400  | Bad Request           |
| 401  | Unauthorized          |
| 403  | Forbidden             |
| 404  | Not Found             |
| 429  | Rate Limited          |
| 500  | Internal Server Error |

📌 Example:

Wrong API Key:

```http
